Simple.source_line: late [Flow Match|Match] -> [Flow Match|Flow Match] (flow "spreads" to adjacent blocks of same color. this repeats until it has no more blocks to spread to. game wins when all blocks on the map can be flowed to from an arbitrary flow placement, i.e. all blocks of the same color are touching)

Message.message: Every non-standard Sokoban mechanic from Sokofun is implemented in this clone. The following levels are recreations of levels that appear in the shareware version of Sokofun, arranged in a way that I hope will make for the best overview and tutorial covering all of the elements.
If everything here is accurate, you can recreate the full, paid version of Sokofun by hacking this game to add different levels.
